 Of Borrowers [ http://www2.ed.gov/documents/press-releases/04282016-cred=
it-reporting.doc ]. *The Department of Education and the Department of th=
e Treasury, in consultation with the CFPB, are working collaboratively wi=
th the credit reporting industry to develop guidance for servicers, lende=
rs, and others who furnish data to the credit bureaus to determine how be=
