</span></span></span><![endif]><b><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;line-heig=
ht:105%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif">Launch of StudentLoans.=
gov/Repay.
</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&qu=
ot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif">To help borrowers easily navigate the complexi=
ty of student loan repayment options, the U.S. Digital Service and the Depa=
rtment of Education&#8217;s Office of Federal Student
 Aid have launched <b>StudentLoans.gov/Repay</b> to help drive students to =
their best repayment option in five steps or less. Built mobile-first, and =
using human-centered design,
<b>StudentLoans.gov/Repay</b> was <span style=3D"color:black">designed to m=
ake repayment information as easy to understand as possible.</span><b><o:p>=
</o:p></b></span></p>
