he most up-to-date information based on
 their circumstances, borrowers would see a plain language Playbook on thei=
r monthly bill, in regular email communications from their student loan ser=
vicer, or when they log into their student loan account. The Department of =
Education, working with the CFPB,
 will be finalizing and implementing these disclosures for federal loans bo=
rrowers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
