ll Borrowers
</span></i><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&qu=
ot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif">through a
</span><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif"><a href=
=3D"http://www2.ed.gov/documents/press-releases/strengthening-student-loan-=
system.pdf"><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%">report</span>=
</a></span><span style=3D"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:105%;font-family:&qu=
